<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>The Normies</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="./media/favicon/icon.png">
    <!--bootstrap-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!--google fonts-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab">
    <!--custom css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark fixed-top">
            <button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#myNavbar" aria-controls="myNavbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                <img src="./media/nav/navbrand.png" width="40" height="40" class="d-inline-block align-top" alt="navbar brand">
                The Normies
            </a>
                    
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="myNavbar">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto mt-2 mt-md-0">
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/clan">Our Clan</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/about">About</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <!--<div class="container-fluid" id="home-slides">-->
        <div id="bannerSlides" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="5000" data-pause="false">
            <div class="carousel-inner" id="bannerInner"></div>
        </div>
    <!--</div>-->
    <main>
        <div class="container" id="wrapper">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3 class="card-header">The Normies</h3>
                        <div class="card-block">
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Here at "The Normies", we dedicate ourselves to spreading our dankness to the farthest reaches of the Clash Royale community.
                                As a clan, we try to get the best participation out of all our members.
                                We pride ourselves on our diversity as a clan that allows us to come together to roast on people of all regions.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3 class="card-header">About Us</h3>
                        <div class="card-block">
                            <p class="card-text">
                                We wreck clans... mostly. We have some s*!t players as well, unfortunately. 
                                We require that every player contribute a little to the clan chest every week.
                                There are also tournaments hosted from time to time for our loyal clan members. The usurper "Pina" is in exile.
                                Feel free to join us if you can contribute to our clan chest.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br/><br/>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h2 class="display-3 card-header">Our Fearless Leader</h2>
                        <div class="card-block" id="leader-home">
                            <h3 class="display-5"><a href="/player/<%=leader.tag%>"><%= leader.name %></a></h3>
                            <p class="lead">Level: <%= leader.expLevel %></p>
                            <p class="lead">Trophies: <%= leader.trophies %></p>
                            <p class="lead">Arena: <%= leader.arena.name %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br/><br/>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h2 class="display-3 card-header">All-Star Clan Chest Earner</h2>
                        <div class="card-block" id="top-clan-earner">
                            <h3 class="display-5"><a href="/player/<%=top.tag%>"><%= top.name %></a></h3>
                            <p class="lead">Level: <%= top.expLevel %></p>
                            <p class="lead">Clan Chest Crowns: <%= top.clanChestCrowns %></p>
                            <p class="lead">Trophies: <%= leader.trophies %></p>
                            <p class="lead">Arena: <%= leader.arena.name %></p>
                            <p class="card-text">Special thanks given to this player for their hard work and contribution to the clan. The rest of our players better step up.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br/><br/>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <% include ./partials/footer %>
    </footer>
</body>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $.getJSON('/files/media/home')
            .done(function(data){
                var i = 0;
                $.each(data, function(key, val){
                    if(i==0){
                        $('#bannerInner').append('<div class="carousel-item active"><img class="d-block w-100 img-fluid" alt="home page background" src="' + val.name + '">');
                    }
                    else{
                        $('#bannerInner').append('<div class="carousel-item"><img class="d-block w-100 img-fluid" alt="home page background" src="' + val.name + '">');
                    }
                    i += 1;
                });
            });
        });
    </script>
</html>